        </div>
        <h3><strong>Real-World Applications</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Fan Game Cube's flexibility makes it practical across multiple sports categories and organizational scales. Whether you're an individual athlete building your brand or a major league managing multiple teams, the platform provides adaptable tokenization solutions tailored to your needs.
        </p>
        <p>
          The magic happens in real-time: live in-game events automatically trigger point rewards for zone owners the moment they occur. This instant connection between physical gameplay and digital ownership creates a level of fan engagement that simply wasn't possible before.
        </p>
        <p>
